### Video Game Collection API - HTTP Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000
### Supported languages: en, fr, es

### ====================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ====================

GET http://localhost:3000/health
Accept-Language: en

###

GET http://localhost:3000/health?lang=fr
Accept-Language: fr

###

### ====================
### CREATE GAME (POST) - 201
### ====================

### Create a new game - English
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en

{
  "title": "The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild",
  "genre": "Action-Adventure",
  "releaseDate": "2017-03-03",
  "platform": "Nintendo Switch"
}

###

### Create a new game - French
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: fr

{
  "title": "Elden Ring",
  "genre": "Action RPG",
  "releaseDate": "2022-02-25",
  "platform": "PC"
}

###

### Create a new game - Spanish
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: es

{
  "title": "Cyberpunk 2077",
  "genre": "Action RPG",
  "releaseDate": "2020-12-10",
  "platform": "PC"
}

###

### Create another game for testing
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Super Mario 64",
  "genre": "Platformer",
  "releaseDate": "1996-06-23",
  "platform": "Nintendo Switch"
