{
  "title": "Incomplete Game"
}

###

### ====================
### GET ALL GAMES (GET) - 200
### ====================

### Get all games in JSON format
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: en

###

### Get all games in XML format
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Accept: application/xml
Accept-Language: en

###

### Get all games in YAML format
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games
Accept: application/yaml
Accept-Language: fr

###

### Get all games with French language
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games?lang=fr
Accept: application/json

###

### ====================
### GET SINGLE GAME (GET) - 200, 404
### ====================

### Get a specific game - ID 1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/1
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: en

###

### Get a specific game in XML
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/1
Accept: application/xml

###

### Get a specific game in YAML
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/1
Accept: application/yaml

###

### Get non-existent game (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/999
Accept: application/json

###

### ====================
### UPDATE GAME (PATCH) - 200, 404
### ====================

### Partial update - Update only title
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en

{
  "title": "The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild (Updated)"
}

###

### Partial update - Update genre and platform
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/2
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: fr

{
  "genre": "Fantasy RPG",
  "platform": "PlayStation"
}

###

### Update non-existent game (404)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Non-existent Game"
}

###

### ====================
### DELETE GAME (DELETE) - 204, 404
### ====================

### Delete a game (no response body expected - 204)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/3

###

### Delete non-existent game (404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/games/999

###

